steps.description:
You stole a relic from a dragon’s hoard. Choose one: 
Weapon – an oversized melee weapon of your choice that deals +1 damage per dragon (or powerful creature) slain; 
Armor – Dragonbane armor that provides 25 Armor and grants immunity to fear effects caused by dragons but cannot be removed once worn;
Trinket – a draconic fear talisman that, once per day, allows you to target a creature within reach and inflict the Fear condition (a creature affected by this talisman cannot be targeted again).
